features: [1-to-2 Extension] The RJ45 1-to-2 Ethernet splitter can help you avoid constantly pulling cables and prevent cable breakage. It can also be used for extension purposes. Without a router, one RJ45 socket can be extended to three standard 8P8C designs, allowing three network cables to be connected into a longer cable with this splitter. However, please note that this splitter is not a router and cannot provide internet access to multiple devices simultaneously. When one device is using the network, other devices may need to be turned off or disconnected.

[Plug-and-Play] The splitter does not require any drivers! Its design makes installation extremely simple and does not require additional settings. With stable signal transmission and excellent contact ability, it ensures successful high-speed data transmission.

[High-Quality Materials] We use a 2mm thick PCB board and 8-core pure copper gold-plated conductor design to ensure excellent performance and durability. It also has a fixed RJ45 female interface, which can effectively shield electromagnetic interference and provide users with a more stable network environment.

[Wide Compatibility] The splitter has wide compatibility, including hubs, ADSL, switches, PS-4, televisions, set-top boxes, routers, wireless devices, and computers. Using this splitter can greatly improve work efficiency, by avoiding frequent cable pulling.

[Peace of Mind Guarantee] If you encounter any problems during use, please do not hesitate to contact us at any time. Our professional team will be happy to help answer your questions and provide solutions. We also conduct regular email follow-ups to ensure your satisfaction with our products. We are available 24 hours a day, year-round. Our team is available 7 days a week via email to provide first-class support.
